The Day My Bum Went Psycho (known in North America as The Day My Butt Went Psycho) is a novel by Australian children's author, Andy Griffiths.The book focuses on a boy called Zack Freeman who has to seek the help of some "bum-hunters" to catch his bum after he learns it is actually the leader of a band of rogue bums determined to control the world. It is illustrated by Nicole Arroyo, who also illustrated some of Andy Griffiths' other books, including the Just! series.